Thanks for listening to Mackenzie Price and the Future of Education podcast.

13:28.420 --> 13:31.220
If you haven't hit that subscribe button, now is the time to do it.

13:31.220 --> 13:34.020
So you can stay up to date on all our episodes.

13:34.020 --> 13:36.180
You can connect with Mackenzie on social media

13:36.180 --> 13:39.060
and be part of our daily conversation over on Instagram

13:39.060 --> 13:42.020
at futureofunderscoreeducation.

13:42.020 --> 13:44.020
Lastly, if you're loving what you're learning,

13:44.020 --> 13:47.220
please leave a review wherever you listen to podcasts.

13:47.220 --> 13:48.580
We'll be back in your feed soon.

13:48.580 --> 13:50.980
But until then, remember, kids are limitless.

13:50.980 --> 13:52.900
And it's our job to unlock their potential.

